Toyota’s production line is operated in “tense flow”, parts arrive every 37 minutes from UK and EU suppliers for custom-made vehicles.
If the UK leaves the EU without a deal on March 29, there could be disruptions at the border that the industry says could lead to delays and shortages of parts.
